channel.title: [PI] Webclient back into client
channel.description: I want to make the cache read from the client folder with the minimum ammount of work possible. So I would have to put the cache in the client folder before I upload it. Because the cachedownloaders broke. All the files it downloads are corrupt. I'm using LostLegacy. Everyone with LostLegacy has a broke cachedownloader.
